    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document provides functional requirements for the support of Metro Ethernet Forum (MEF) Ethernet Tree (E-Tree) in multipoint Layer 2 Virtual Private Network solutions (referred to as simply "L2VPN").  It is intended that potential solutions will use these requirements as guidelines.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
